 尼泊爾病毒株流入社區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2282758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2282758</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ad8333613c16297175f5655132dec31f11c21912","tid":2283112,"uid":273360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人唔笑連狗都吠"},{"pid":"1ec99123323cf3e68843f5a8c61dc557e9ca2e47","tid":2283112,"uid":239086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b59a97f075f6e6c88b60aae7510bbe67dc0c6b82","tid":2283112,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:04:46.000Z","msg":"賺錢唔報稅<br />\n無錢搵要政府救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:29:24.000Z","msg":"人哋有交稅，不過交晒俾阿公啫⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家無生意咪搵返阿公攞囉，問政府做乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781238d866a124b47b796ab895782b9243449c79","tid":2283112,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"893b9782c2b3a9f7d77c17f8d68e96a2a937d70a","tid":2283112,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"疫情下，油麻地多個粵曲文化劇社在限聚令下，被迫停業最少五個月，期間警方到時通知他們必須停業，百多個從業員多月來零收入，檔主亦要每月自費數萬元交租，生活大受影響。一班檔主及歌手今日（12日）到政府總部向政務司司長張建宗遞交請願信，望有關方面了解行業困難，將一班歌手及檔主納入防疫抗疫基金受支助行列，共渡時艱。<br />\n<br />\n疫情下，市面上各行各業受到不同程度的影響，一班於油麻地廟街開設歌舞廳的負責人及從業員，因受制於限聚令之下，被迫兩度停業，但由於他們未有申請娛樂場所牌照，未能獲得防疫抗疫基金的支援，要自費繳交大約每個月5萬元的租金及其他雜費，大嘆難以維持。其中一名檔主徐小姐表示，擔心疫情仍然未能受控，可能會發生第四波疫情，歌唱廳有可能會因此倒閉。<br />\n<br />\n徐小姐續説，第三輪防疫抗疫基金下，卡拉OK及酒吧等處所均可獲發25000元一次性資助，公眾娛樂場所亦獲資助1萬及5萬元不等。但歌龐歌廊雖然被要求停業，卻完全不獲任何補貼支援，感覺被忽視。<br />\n<br />\n另一名檔主廖小姐表示，歌手主要是多勞多得，收入大多不穩定，返工時間大多分為三間制，凌晨12時至清晨5時為最後一更，現時只能夠營業至凌晨二時下，部份表演者根本沒有收入，連月來損失約萬元。「我哋明白到係因為我哋一直無供強積金之下，唔能夠受惠保就業基金，但係而家嘅收入的而且確受到影響，好難繼續捱落去。」期望政府能夠協助業界及這個傳統行業發展，將他們納入受影響一群。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201112/403531983767998464186903.jpeg/yK-VG-ZsWbJfnBOrbQNaV9Sn_u4amqecb8kbN2_JGzc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201112%2F403531983767998464186903.jpeg%2FyK-VG-ZsWbJfnBOrbQNaV9Sn_u4amqecb8kbN2_JGzc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=b78f3a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201112/403532645398482944087612.jpeg/zLf_AZi--clMzo1WuPqRmloBK5gsG7FbAxrGjyUaxo8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201112%2F403532645398482944087612.jpeg%2FzLf_AZi--clMzo1WuPqRmloBK5gsG7FbAxrGjyUaxo8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7ca192d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n檔主廖小姐表示，連月來要自費繳交約五萬元的租金，感到吃力。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a572f32dcbc0157b6cd314ce0463f08e67271e","tid":2283112,"uid":332452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e47a2807e916cee2e604a0abf8ad94acb7a51ed","tid":2283112,"uid":97863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"出糧出火發鳩痕～"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:33:20.000Z","msg":"落廟街搵女人～"},{"pid":"0185879602a19f27170b55047e7cf3eacc6f32a2","tid":2283112,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T12:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa0be5f9c33c490af593b541ee2759bc72de183","tid":2283112,"uid":258960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12